The paper discusses the application of machine learning algorithms and word embeddings for hierarchical text classification, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL). The use of word embeddings and deep learning models also suggests a focus on deep learning (cs.DL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
